                <list id="11" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Noto Sans&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click </text><text styleclass="Element">Line</text><image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">- it is in the </text><text styleclass="Element">Part</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> that is kinematically-defined. </text></li>
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click </text><text styleclass="Element">Line</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> &#160;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">- it is in the </text><text styleclass="Element">Part</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> that is </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">NOT</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> kinematically-defined. </text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <list id="12" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Complete the Command </li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="13" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="4" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager:</text> &#160;<text styleclass="HowTo STEP">Click </text><image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo STEP" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo STEP"> in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</text><text styleclass="HowTo STEP">.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text style="font-weight:normal;">The </text><text styleclass="Element">Rack-Pinion</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> is now in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Assembly-Tree</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> and </text><text styleclass="Interface">Graphic-Area</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Interface2">Result</text> : </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text style="font-weight:normal;">The </text><text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> is on the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Rotating-Part</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text style="font-weight:normal;">The </text><text styleclass="Element">Rack</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> is on the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Sliding-Part</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The Pitch-Line of the <text styleclass="Element">Rack</text> is parallel to the <text styleclass="Element">Line</text><image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets" figurelistinclude="0"></image> you select in for the <text styleclass="VariableName">Slide-Joint</text> and <text styleclass="VariableName">Sliding-Part</text>. </para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The Pitch-Line of the <text styleclass="Element">Rack</text> is tangential with the <text styleclass="Element">Pitch-Circle</text> of the Pinion.</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The Pitch-Line of the <text styleclass="Element">Rack</text> is offset from the center of the <text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text> by the <text styleclass="VariableName">Pitch-Circle Radius</text> of the <text styleclass="Element">Pinion</text>.</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text style="font-weight:normal;">The </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Rotating-Part</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> is now a </text><text styleclass="Element">Part</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> that is </text><text styleclass="Interface">kinematically-defined</text><text style="font-weight:normal;">.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:240px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-DRIVINGRACK-PINION-0.ipp" scale="-99.90%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
